introduction: The video discusses the concept of responsible quantum computing and the principles that guide its development and deployment. The speaker highlights the importance of collaboration, awareness, and partnerships in ensuring a secure and responsible use of quantum technologies.

sections.title: Section 1: Introduction to Responsible Quantum Computing
content: Explanation of the term 'responsible quantum computing'
Importance of responsible quantum computing for the future of technology and society
Overview of the five principles that guide responsible quantum computing
Explanation of the role of IBM Quantum Safe Explorer in identifying and managing cryptography in systems

sections.title: Section 2: Discovering and Managing Cryptography in Systems
content: Explanation of the role of IBM Quantum Safe Explorer in discovering cryptography artifacts in systems
Description of the dynamic cryptography exchange program called Fund Portfolio Analysis
Discussion of the importance of observing dynamic cryptography exchange in network systems
Explanation of how IBM Quantum Safe Explorer can be used to augment cryptography management policies

sections.title: Section 3: The Role of Awareness in Responsible Quantum Computing
content: Explanation of the importance of awareness in ensuring responsible quantum computing
Discussion of the lack of awareness in many companies and the need for conversation with suppliers
Overview of the partnerships and capabilities that can help address the challenges of responsible quantum computing
Emphasis on the need for planning and collaboration in addressing the complex transformational journey ahead

sections.title: Section 4: The Global Impact of Responsible Quantum Computing
content: Explanation of the global impact of responsible quantum computing on various industries and sectors
Discussion of the need for collaboration and partnerships across enterprises to ensure responsible quantum computing
Overview of the challenges and costs associated with responsible quantum computing
Emphasis on the importance of starting the conversation and taking action now
topics: Global Impact of Responsible Quantum Computing

sections.title: Section 5: Conclusion and Call to Action
content: Recap of the key points discussed in the video
Emphasis on the need for responsible quantum computing to address the challenges of the future
Call to action for viewers to start the conversation and take action towards responsible quantum computing
Thank you message for the audience's time and attention
